dataList.dlg: А выстоишь ли ты этот удар?

Too late… They’ve all been captivated.
Alright, try enduring this... It'll fry you just enough to kill.

Allow me... to introduce you to this manor...
Butlers... Where are the stewards of this house? You must know... Lead me to them, now!

I can do nothing but mourn for them.
